race.description: Bet365 Bet Boost Highweight Maiden Plate
race.comment: Very modest race even for a highweight and CITY WOK (1) won't get a better chance to break through. Beaten only three lengths in a 60k maiden latest and fifth prior to that, also in a better race. This suits ideally. HIGHLAND DASH (10) finished out of the money on debut two starts back then she was never in contention and was beaten 10 lengths when eighth in a 1618m contest at Werribee last time. Blinkers added and this is easier. Has upside and looks a leading chance. Same goes for AURELIO (7) who has upside after a fair debut when beaten six lengths at big odds. Will find this much easier. SOMETHING SUPER (6) is on the quick back-up after a poor run in the latest and last two have been below par but the run three back puts him right in this. OTTO'S DREAM (9) was beaten a long way at debut but can only improve in this easier company.
